
MOVIE BOOKING APPLICATION

 üìå Problem Statement

Design a Movie Booking Application using Object-Oriented Programming (OOP) concepts.

The application should allow users to:

1. Book movie tickets
2. Calculate total ticket price based on movie type
3. Validate seat booking
4. Support multiple movie categories with different pricing logic


